line_1: Th' Imperial Eagle and the Pontiff rag'd;
line_2: Europe was in destructive wars engag'd,

line_1: Oh! if ye ever yet have rag'd,
line_2: Ye well will guess the war we wag'd,

line_1: And conscious villains trembled as he rag'd.
line_2: With dauntless warmth in Virtue's cause engag'd,

line_1: Which fann'd by pow'r, o'er wasted nations rag'd.
line_2: So wou'd that flame have mimick fights engag'd,
